    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Ok so I don't want to create a new widget.\nI want to init `instantsearch.js` with a predefined numeric filter.\nSomething like:\n\n``` js\nvar search = instantsearch({\n  appId: 'APP_ID',\n  apiKey: 'API_KEY',\n  indexName: 'INDEX_NAME',\n  searchParameters: ??????? // price > 50\n});\n```\n\nIt's not explained in [the documentation](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/documentation/#initialization)\n",
    "created_at": "2016-09-08T07:01:48Z",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/1264#issuecomment-245511311",
